fields.name: Free the Tipple: Kickass Cocktails Inspired by Iconic Women
fields.description: Written by Jennifer Croll. Sixty of the world's coolest and most influential women are the inspiration for this refreshing and fun collection of drink recipes that are sure to bring extra zest to your cocktail shaker.

fields.name: Tiki: Modern Tropical Cocktails
fields.description: Written by Shannon Mustipher. With original recipes, techniques, tasting notes and recommendations, and tips on style and music, Tiki is an inspirational resource for cocktail lovers ready to explore fine Caribbean rums.

fields.name: The Bar Book: Elements of Cocktail Technique
fields.description: Written by Jeffrey Morgenthaler. This indispensable guide breaks down bartending into essential techniques, and then applies them to building the best drinks. More than 60 recipes illustrate the concepts explored in the text, ranging from juicing, garnishing, carbonating, stirring, and shaking to choosing the correct ice for proper chilling and dilution of a drink.

fields.name: The Complete Home Bartender's Guide
